<h3>Hashing and salting</h3>
<br />
<span
  >Hashing a password is putting a password through a hashing algorithm to
  convert the password(a string) into many random characters, letters and
  numbers.</span
>
<br />
<span
  >Salting a password is adding a extra layer of security to a password. It add
  a sequence of random character at the end of a password making it harder to
  crack.</span
><br />

